                    </div>
                    <span>I found this book to be written in a very basic, generic writing<BR>style. Much better books have been written on this subject in a<BR>much more interesting way. No new information here I have'nt read elsewhere. This book should have been titled "Hollywood <BR>Book of Death For Dummies" or something. I highly recommend this<BR>book for the Hollywood graveyard beginner. Enjoy.</span>
                  
              
